dataset - Variable in class NonRotamericLibrary
Data is stored in this nested structure: BackboneAngles(phi,psi) --> DiscreteProbabilityDistribution( NonRotamericAngles, Double probabilities ) where NonRotamericAngles is a List of chis and a DiscreteProbabilityDistribution in the last non-rotameric angle.
dataset - Variable in class RotamericLibrary
Data storage is accomplished using map from back bone angles to each rotamer (list of chis) (phi, psi) ---> [[ X1, X2, ..., Xn ], probability of this rotamer]
